  <paragraph l10n="U" role="paragraph" id="par_id3153255" xml-lang="en-US" oldref="2"><ahelp visibility="visible" hid=".uno:ColorControl">Show or hides the <emph>Color Bar</emph>. To modify or change the color table that is displayed, choose <emph>Format â€“ Area</emph>, and then click on the <emph>Colors </emph>tab.</ahelp></paragraph>
